  <summary date="2022-08-30T21:22:37Z" status="Passed Senate">Recycling Infrastructure and Accessibility Act of 2022

This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) to establish a pilot grant program for improving recycling accessibility in communities. The EPA may award grants to states, local governments, Indian tribes, or public-private partnerships.</summary>
